articles.author: Barak Ravid
articles.title: U.S. says "further progress was made" in third round of nuclear talks with Iran - Axios
articles.description: Talks on Saturday were the first time parties dived into technical details of a possible nuclear deal.
articles.content:
The U.S. and Iran concluded on Saturday the third round of nuclear talks and agreed to meet again on May 3, said Omani foreign minister Badr Al-Busaidi, who is mediating between the parties.
